Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.38,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:258420,261380}Looks like Nariki's nibbling on the basics.{NOTE:ナリキさん食らい付いてってるゴロニャ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.13,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:261380,263130}Hang in there-nyaa.{NOTE:ファイトでしゅニャ｡}
