Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.84,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:264260,265840}Ah, it's you, Mille.{NOTE:あっミルさん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.97,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:265840,267970}What are those two up to?{NOTE:ナリキたち何してんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.89,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:267970,269890}They're training.{NOTE:訓練だゴロニャ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.56,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:269890,273560}Beats is trying to fire Nariki up.{NOTE:ビーツがナリキさんに気合を入れてるんでしゅニャ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:50.20,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:285820,290200}Even if your Velocidrome can dodge it,\Nit's no use if you can't dodge it too.{NOTE:ドスランポスがよけられてもお前がよけられなきゃ意味ねえだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.33,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:290200,291330}Listen!{NOTE:いいか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:55.50,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:291330,295500}A Rider and their Monstie must be one in both mind and body!{NOTE:ライダーとオトモンは一心同体でなきゃいけねえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.08,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:295500,297080}Got it?{NOTE:分かるか?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.13,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:297080,299130}Y-Yeah.{NOTE:う…うっす｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.17,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:299130,301170}Alright! Next!{NOTE:もういい！次だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.80,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:302300,304800}This time we'll train your jumping.{NOTE:次はジャンプの訓練だ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.55,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:304800,307550}Jump over that obstacle while running at full speed.{NOTE:全力疾走であの障害を跳び越えろ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.76,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:307550,308760}Got it.{NOTE:うっす｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.93,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:308760,310930}Good luck-nyaa…{NOTE:頑張るでしゅニャ～｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.93,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:311930,313930}You can do it, Drome.{NOTE:いけるよな？ランポ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.15,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:315100,317150}All right, let's go, Drome!{NOTE:よし！行けランポ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.90,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:319480,320900}Alright! Jump!{NOTE:よし！跳べ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.59,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:341340,343590}This should be okay for now.{NOTE:取りあえずこれでよしっと｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.76,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:343590,344760}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.97,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:344760,346970}Y-Yeah…{NOTE:うっす…}
