Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.01,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:349850,351010}I guess you're not okay…{NOTE:だいじょばないね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.31,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:353060,354310}Tsk.{NOTE:チッ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.48,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:354310,355480}How pathetic.{NOTE:情けねえ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.69,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:359520,360690}Beats…{NOTE:ビーツ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.98,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:360690,362980}Nariki is still learning.{NOTE:ナリキはライダーになりたてなんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.53,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:362980,365530}Be a little more understanding.{NOTE:もうちょっと優しくしてあげなよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.74,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:365530,367740}I have to be tough on him.{NOTE:厳しくしなきゃ駄目だ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.03,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:367740,369030}Beats…{NOTE:ビーツ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.12,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:370280,372120}Don't you get it?{NOTE:だってそうだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.12,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:372120,375120}The Ebon Riders are still hunting for Kinship Stones.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズが絆石狩りしてるってのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.25,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:375120,377250}And we can't get help from Lute or anyone else.{NOTE:…リュートたちは村にいない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.25,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:377250,380250}Pampering isn't a luxury that Nariki gets right now.{NOTE:そんなときに甘やかす時間なんかないんだよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.42,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:380250,382420}You sure are strict.{NOTE:ビーツは厳しいゴロニャ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.84,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:382420,384840}I feel sorry for Nariki-nyaa.{NOTE:ナリキさんがかわいそうでしゅニャ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.76,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:384840,385760}Hmph.{NOTE:フン｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:39.23,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:395140,399230}You know, Drome… you could listen to me a little more.{NOTE:ランポ…お前もう少し言うこと聞いてくれよな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.69,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:401310,402690}Okay?{NOTE:いいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:48.65,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:402690,408650}Me, Mille and Hyoro are the only ones\Nin the village with Kinship Stones.{NOTE:村で絆石持ってるのもう自分とミル先輩ヒョロ先輩しか残ってないんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.37,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:408650,411370}So we can't take it slow right now.{NOTE:気長になんてやってられないんだぞ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.91,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:412570,414910}Are you even listening?{NOTE:お前話聞いてないだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.29,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:418000,419290}What's wrong, Nariki?{NOTE:どうした？ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.00,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:419290,421000}I heard you sighing.{NOTE:ため息なんかついて｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.54,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:421000,422540}Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:07.26,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:422540,427260}I know you want to get strong right now,\Nbut you shouldn't rush it.{NOTE:強くなりたいという気持ちは分かるが焦りは禁物だぞ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.05,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:427260,429050}Don't rush it, huh…{NOTE:焦りっつうか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.60,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:432140,434600}Aren't Velocidromes pretty weak?{NOTE:ドスランポスって弱くないっすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.22,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:434600,436220}Hey, hey.{NOTE:待て待て｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.48,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:436220,439480}Velocidrome is a nice and easy to handle Monstie.{NOTE:ドスランポスは扱いやすいいいオトモンだぞ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.06,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:439480,442060}I can't handle it at all though.{NOTE:全然扱いやすくないっすよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.27,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:442060,445270}He has no breaths and he can't fly either.{NOTE:ブレスも吐けないし空も飛べない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.90,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:445270,448900}No much how hard we try, this Monstie…{NOTE:オトモンがそんなんじゃいくら頑張ったところで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.78,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:448900,452780}Hey! A Monstie's strength doesn't come from its attacks.{NOTE:こら！オトモンの強さはモンスターの強さじゃない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.83,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:452780,455830}It's built on the kinship with their Riders.{NOTE:ライダーとオトモンの絆の力だ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:40.46,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:455830,460460}Besides, Velocidromes are much\Nfaster than most monsters.{NOTE:それにドスランポスはスピードならたいていのモンスターよりも速い｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:44.71,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:460460,464710}Beats-Senpai says so too,\Nbut tapping into that speed isn't easy.{NOTE:ビーツ先輩もそう言うけど簡単にできないっす｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.04,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:464710,466040}I have no talent for it.{NOTE:才能ないんす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.10,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:474760,477100}I'm sorry, Nariki.{NOTE:すまんなナリキ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.22,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:477100,479220}I'm the one who dragged you into this.{NOTE:お前には無理をさせている｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.69,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:480180,483690}Normally the defense of the village is our job.{NOTE:本来なら村の守りは俺たちの仕事だ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.19,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:483690,486190}But, we let them take our Kinship Stones…{NOTE:だが俺たちの絆石は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:12.61,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:487820,492610}Mille and Hyoro will also leave the\hvillage soon to help Lute's group.{NOTE:ミルもヒョロもリュートたちを助けるためにまた村を出ていくだろう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:17.12,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:492610,497120}At that time you will be the only Rider left in this village.{NOTE:そうなったらこの村に残されたライダーはお前だけなんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.16,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:497120,500160}So I know how hard it is, but please do your best.{NOTE:だからつらいのは分かるが頑張ってくれ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.50,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:502080,503500}I understand.{NOTE:分かったっす｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.88,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:503500,505880}I will do my best for the sake of our village.{NOTE:自分村のために頑張るっす｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.79,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:506920,507790}Sorry.{NOTE:すまん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.22,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:513380,515220}Come on, come on!{NOTE:そらそら！どうした！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.18,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:515220,517180}Increase your speed!{NOTE:もっとスピードを上げろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.52,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:517180,519520}Drome, let's go faster!{NOTE:ランポ！もっと速くだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.39,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:523060,524390}{\i1}Stronger…{NOTE:もっとだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.10,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:524390,526100}{\i1}I need to get stronger.{NOTE:もっと強くなるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.32,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:532990,537320}{\i1}When that happens, we'll be able to get our seniors' Kinship Stones back.{NOTE:強くなって先輩たちの絆石を取り戻すんだ。}
