Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.96,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:543120,545960}When you go that fast,\Nyou have to give out orders sooner!{NOTE:スピードを出すなら指示は早めに出さないと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.88,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:549500,550880}Drome! Righ—{NOTE:ランポ！右だ—}
