Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.37,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:576610,578370}Don't take out your anger on him, Nariki.{NOTE:八つ当たりはよせ！ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.99,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:579200,581990}It's not Drome's fault.{NOTE:うまくいかないのはランポのせいじゃないだろう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.45,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:581990,583450}Ah…{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:47.96,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:583450,587960}You're trying to become faster and stronger, but…{NOTE:お前は自分勝手に速くなろう強くなろうとしているが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.96,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:587960,590960}…unless you change your attitude…{NOTE:…その独り善がりな気持ちをあらためないかぎり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:54.97,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:590960,594970}…Drome will never listen to you.{NOTE:…いつまでたってもランポはお前の言うことを聞いてはくれないぞ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:01.39,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:597430,601390}What's important is strengthening your kinship.{NOTE:大事なことはオトモンとの絆を強くすることだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:05.77,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:601390,605770}Everything else will come naturally after that.{NOTE:そうすれば強さとか速さは自然と後からついてくる｡}
