Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.57,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:611320,613570}Hey, I can't hear you!{NOTE:おい！返事が聞こえねえぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.20,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:615900,618200}I get it…{NOTE:言ってることは分かるんすけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.87,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:618200,619870}…but you're {\fs40}g{\fs39}e{\fs38}t{\fs37}t{\fs36}i{\fs35}n{\fs34}g {\fs33}o{\fs32}n {\fs31}m{\fs30}y {\fs29}n{\fs28}e{\fs27}r{\fs26}v{\fs25}e{\fs24}s.{NOTE:…言い方がうざいんすよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.54,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:621030,623540}I said, you're getting on my nerves!{NOTE:だからうざいっす！}
