Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:40.68,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:635300,640680}Kinship this, kinship that! You're not even a Rider so what do you understand about Monsties?{NOTE:絆絆って｡ライダーでもないくせにオトモンの何が分かるんだよ！}
