Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.47,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:642720,644470}Ah yes, I did!{NOTE:ああ言ったさ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.31,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:647730,650310}All right, fine, do whatever then!{NOTE:だったら勝手にしろってんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.11,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:650310,652110}Yeah, just watch me!{NOTE:ああ勝手にするさ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.95,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:662320,664950}I wonder how Nariki's doing?{NOTE:ナリキさん大丈夫ゴロニャ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.62,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:664950,668620}He's fine. He's very motivated-nyaa.{NOTE:大丈夫でしゅニャ｡張り切ってましたから｡}
